imdb.plot outline: With Sophie, no two voyages are alike. Born blind, however, armed with optimism and a genuine desire for adventure, Sophie, always accompanied by her trusted Dalmatian guide dog, Pongo, she sets out to discover the world that we live in through her senses and the eyes of her travelling companions. In the same way, we will travel alongside with the intrepid journalist in her journey to the four corners of the world, in order to explore the different cultures, mingle with the everyday people and share their activities, in this unique and unexpected travel guide. Ultimately, as we participate in Sophie's sensational voyage, we will re-evaluate the way we relate to others, question the way we perceive our environment and above all, embrace life's diversity through a different perspective.
imdb.title: Dans tes yeux
